The '''Twomi Skyfire''' was a kind of ship that had the engines of a racer, the lines of a starfighter and designed to make the occasional pilot comfortable at the controls. They came with automatic landing, navigation, crash and collision avoidance overrides and voice assisted preflight. The ''[[Jump For Joy]]'' was a Twomi Skyfire.

